The paper discusses the integration of artificial neural networks (ANNs) and machine learning in wireless communications, making it highly likely to belong to the cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) sub-category. Additionally, the paper covers topics related to information theory (cs.IT), machine learning (cs.LG and cs.AI), and control systems (cs.SY) in the context of wireless networks.
